sequenceDiagram
    participant C as 客户端
    participant G as API Gateway
    participant RL as 限流 Redis
    participant S as Go 接入服务
    participant IR as 库存 Redis

    C->>G: token + request_id=R1
    G->>RL: claim(nonce, R1)
    RL-->>G: FIRST_USE
    G->>S: 新请求
    S->>IR: 预占
    IR-->>S: reservation_id=RS1
    S-->>C: QUEUED

    C->>G: token + request_id=R1
    G->>RL: claim(nonce, R1)
    RL-->>G: SAME_REQUEST_RETRY
    G->>S: 查询 R1 原始结果
    S->>IR: 查询 request_id=R1
    IR-->>S: QUEUED / RS1
    S-->>C: 返回第一次请求结果
